  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One arrested with tear gas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person who was in possession of 50 tear gas shells was arrested yesterday.",
        "The suspect has been arrested by the Welikada Police in Obeysekarapura, Nanayakkara Mawathi and after the investigations conducted against him, the said bombs have been recovered from a house in Boralai-Kotami area.",
        "On the night of the 13th of this month, during the protest that took place near the Politua junction of the parliamentary constituency of Weligada Police Division, the suspect attacked two policemen who were on their way to the scene with tear gas canisters and took away the tear gas canisters from them."
      ],
